WEBVTT

00:06.895 --> 00:08.737
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>The Borgias...</i>

00:08.738 --> 00:11.477
<i>ALEXANDER:</i>
<i>Now is the time of reckoning.</i>

00:11.478 --> 00:14.014
The vultures are
circling our family.

00:14.049 --> 00:15.315
Our Rome.

00:15.417 --> 00:18.153
We must remove him from
the chair of St. Peter's-

00:18.220 --> 00:19.753
and from this world.

00:19.788 --> 00:21.789
Vengeance is mine,
saieth the Lord.

00:21.890 --> 00:24.524
Ah, vengeance will be ours.

00:24.592 --> 00:26.693
[♪]

00:27.796 --> 00:28.930
<i>CATHERINA:</i>
<i>No!</i>

00:28.964 --> 00:30.498
<i>ALEXANDER:</i>
<i>Catherina Sforza.</i>

00:30.533 --> 00:32.500
If she does not
kiss the papal ring,

00:32.601 --> 00:35.237
we will drag her in chains
through the streets of Rome!

00:35.305 --> 00:37.073
You would have me kneel to him?

00:37.141 --> 00:38.141
<i>Bow?</i>

00:38.242 --> 00:40.210
<i>I only kneel</i>
<i>when it suits me.</i>

00:40.244 --> 00:42.780
<i>CESARE: Catherina Sforza</i>
<i>shared her bed with me.</i>

00:42.848 --> 00:44.982
Did she beg to be
friends with us?

00:45.016 --> 00:46.851
<i>CESARE:</i>
<i>She remains an enemy.</i>

00:46.886 --> 00:49.889
Now we're in need
of another alliance!

00:49.990 --> 00:51.323
I will not marry.

00:51.358 --> 00:54.694
It is a daughter's duty to
marry her father's choice!

00:54.795 --> 00:56.163
<i>JUAN:</i>
<i>Surrender to my forces!</i>

00:56.231 --> 00:57.564
Journey to Rome!

00:57.598 --> 01:01.068
I will never bend my knee
to the whore master of Rome.

01:01.169 --> 01:02.503
Fire!

01:02.538 --> 01:04.504
We are under attack!

01:04.540 --> 01:06.808
<i>ALEXANDER: What should have</i>
<i>been a glorious victory</i>

01:06.842 --> 01:08.811
is an ignominious defeat.

01:08.878 --> 01:10.412
<i>CESARE: Father, we must</i>
<i>discuss our brother.</i>

01:10.447 --> 01:11.881
<i>He is hurtling towards ruin.</i>

01:11.915 --> 01:13.349
<i>He will drag this</i>
<i>whole family with him.</i>

01:13.450 --> 01:14.984
Sleep well.

01:16.620 --> 01:18.355
[screaming]

01:18.422 --> 01:20.724
<i>DELLA ROVERE: The pope is</i>
<i>surrounded by a ring of steel.</i>

01:20.792 --> 01:23.827
I propose we use the weapon
the Borgia family uses -

01:23.895 --> 01:25.162
<i>Canterella.</i>

01:25.197 --> 01:26.631
<i>ANTONELLO: I would gladly</i>
<i>die to rid the world</i>

01:26.699 --> 01:28.433
of the Borgia pope.

01:28.468 --> 01:30.736
<i>LUCREZIA: The thought</i>
<i>of marriage turns my stomach.</i>

01:30.804 --> 01:33.739
<i>The warm touch of a lover</i>
<i>might ease the pain.</i>

01:33.806 --> 01:35.508
We grow weary of this game.

01:35.542 --> 01:36.743
It is no game.

01:36.810 --> 01:39.345
You are marrying for
all of us, Lucrezia!

01:39.379 --> 01:40.446
For family!

01:40.480 --> 01:41.613
<i>LUCREZIA:</i>
<i>Who are you?</i>

01:41.648 --> 01:43.182
<i>I'm Prince</i>
<i>Alfonso d'Aragona,</i>

01:43.249 --> 01:45.017
suitor to the
Lady Lucrezia.

01:45.085 --> 01:46.352
Yes, I will marry him.

01:46.386 --> 01:49.655
<i>He has all the sweetness</i>
<i>of an apple on the tree.</i>

01:49.722 --> 01:52.824
<i>JUAN: You want to inhabit</i>
<i>my shoes, carry my sword.</i>

01:52.925 --> 01:54.459
You must resign
yourself, Cesare.

01:54.560 --> 01:56.294
One day you'll realize
that everything I've done

01:56.362 --> 01:57.528
has been for your own good.

01:57.563 --> 01:58.830
Leave my baby!

01:58.931 --> 02:00.098
[baby crying]

02:00.166 --> 02:01.466
Juan, leave my
baby alone!

02:01.567 --> 02:03.268
I will not have this
family torn apart!

02:03.369 --> 02:05.169
<i>Help him through</i>
<i>his dark night.</i>

02:05.204 --> 02:07.271
Have you come to beg
forgiveness for your insult?

02:07.339 --> 02:09.006
You're already forgiven.

02:09.041 --> 02:11.476
[gasping in pain]

02:11.544 --> 02:13.211
We're Borgias.

02:13.279 --> 02:14.747
We never forgive.

02:14.814 --> 02:16.215
[gasping in pain]

02:19.486 --> 02:21.821
<i>ALEXANDER: Your brother</i>
<i>murdered in cold blood.</i>

02:21.922 --> 02:23.490
<i>Who would do such a thing?</i>

02:23.591 --> 02:24.891
Many people, Father.

02:24.959 --> 02:27.561
I have wished him
dead a thousand times.

02:27.628 --> 02:28.929
<i>ALEXANDER:</i>
<i>Find his murderer.</i>

02:28.996 --> 02:30.464
Scour all Italy!

02:30.565 --> 02:31.765
There will be no need of that.

02:31.766 --> 02:33.467
Do you know who did this?

02:33.535 --> 02:34.869
<i>CESARE: I have</i>
<i>taken upon my head</i>

02:34.936 --> 02:37.104
<i>the act that none other</i>
<i>would dare commit.</i>

02:37.172 --> 02:39.106
<i>If I cannot have</i>
<i>your affection,</i>

02:39.174 --> 02:41.308
<i>can you at least grant</i>
<i>me your forgiveness?</i>

02:41.376 --> 02:42.743
<i>ALEXANDER:</i>
<i>We realize now</i>

02:42.811 --> 02:44.678
<i>that we have brought</i>
<i>this upon ourselves.</i>

02:48.683 --> 02:50.918
[choking]

02:50.986 --> 02:53.021
FATHER!

02:53.089 --> 02:54.456
HELP!

02:57.460 --> 02:59.470
[♪]

02:59.495 --> 03:03.495
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Borgias 3x01 ♪ </font>
<font color=#00FFFF>The Face of Death</font>
